{"tid":656251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5年間以假冒戶口偷公司近3000萬 助理會計經理原來是通緝犯","createTime":"2018-05-07T05:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T08:40:41.000Z","uid":150685,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"65e866db9a8334df9d3017694f46fbe838a44b2a","tid":656251,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"政府電子貿易服務供應商的助理會計經理，偷偷開設與公司名字相似的銀行戶口，成功將客戶的支票存入假冒戶口，5年間成功盜去2,958萬元。警方將他拘捕後揭發經理過往在一宗盜竊案受審期間棄保潛逃，實為被通緝人士。經理今在高院承認一項盜竊罪，被判監禁5年10個月，法官並下令他禁止出任任何公司的董事或經理15年。<br />\n<br />\n法官在判刑時指，被告梁志源（45歲）的犯案手相對簡單，利用名字相同的公司作為工具，而銀行職員又大意沒察覺。被告於2008年同樣以「穿櫃桶」的方式盜竊公司逾400萬元，手法涉及假文件。<br />\n<br />\n法官又指，僱主需要依賴有誠信的會計團隊去管理資金，被告得到公司信任才能出任該職。惟觀被告的犯罪歷史顯示他不能誠實做人，任何經被告手中的錢都有風險。<br />\n被告稱有賭癮，但兩份心理科醫生報告不認為被告是病態賭徒，法官指被告純粹是個賊，將偷來的盡情錢揮霍。<br />\n<br />\n被告承認於2010至2015年間，偷去標奧電子商務有限公司2,958萬元。<br />\n而被告早年涉及的盜竊案，則早前已被判入獄4年8個月，被告正在服刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180507/58162147\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180507%2F58162147&d=9wiCCIPEbKP8v7XMGyRO%2B%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3ffcd00b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180507%2F58162147&h=7852f399\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180507/58162147</a>"},{"pid":"fa33700314e0155807e27a2d73f06bf748a0430b","tid":656251,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:36:05.000Z","msg":"公司唔知唔見錢㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38987882403ae4833fe357a9ac1e0bc4d4046591","tid":656251,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa33700314e0155807e27a2d73f06bf748a0430b","tid":656251,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:36:05.000Z","msg":"公司唔知唔見錢㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:37:52.000Z","msg":"自己比自己旗下公司可能真係唔會唔知<br />\n通常對家收唔到錢先會瓜瓜叫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2be5edf60048b07ff8757ab7d3c6a3ccb600f8","tid":656251,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fa33700314e0155807e27a2d73f06bf748a0430b","tid":656251,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:36:05.000Z","msg":"公司唔知唔見錢㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"可能資金出入好大<br />\n<br />\n會計可以出到古惑,有d未入帳數,同入帳數,都會登同一會計報表<br />\n<br />\n可能老闆懶,只睇大數就出事"},{"pid":"3a33add764a9dcfdf0653e37adf221a1be2ca686","tid":656251,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T06:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個老闆好信佢班會計"},{"pid":"f3b205a60108dc31efd984f050dc2217ed51ef36","tid":656251,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a33add764a9dcfdf0653e37adf221a1be2ca686","tid":656251,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T06:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個老闆好信佢班會計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T06:41:28.000Z","msg":"有d老闆只睇數唔會理<br />\n特別係富二代<br />\n<br />\n可能會計表都有條數，但寫未入帳之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7758d9fdb0bf62b356d0e96b0b50258459372447","tid":656251,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:37:19.000Z","msg":"喺香港真係唔中六合彩唔犯法唔靠父母幹，喺短時間內搵唔到幾千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6870242ef207faab7686c58a3714b5cdc74a977","tid":656251,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:40:41.000Z","msg":